data.description: New listing available in DESIRABLE and picturesque Oak Creek community - fabulous wooded lots - featuring large community pool, tennis courts, clubhouse, walking path, playground and pond!  ~~ This 3,086-sq-foot brick & cedar home features additional living space in the finished basement, & is set on nearly one full acre.  ~~ FRESHLY-PAINTED and BRAND NEW CARPET just installed - truly move-in ready!!!    ~~  An ABUNDANCE of LARGE WINDOWS offer nature views from every room -- so much natural light to enjoy - so light & bright!   Main floor features LARGE kitchen with upgraded cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and granite counters -- with plenty of space to add an island!  Two-story family room with more windows and gas-starter fireplace.   Main floor office has convenient pocket doors!   ~~~  SPACIOUS master bedroom boasts plantation shutters, tray ceiling, and dual closets.  Three additional bedrooms on the second floor with generous room dimensions! ~~ Basement is partially-finished, includes a 4-person sauna (!) and was upgraded with an extensive whole house water filtration system.  Massive deck is constructed with maintenance-free composite materials - relax & enjoy all the views of nature in your backyard - yard is equipped with automatic sprinkler system!  Don't delay, make your appointment today!
